DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260706T180000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260706T200000
SUMMARY:Conscious Conversations & Somatic Practices  
DESCRIPTION:Iama Embodied Community\nThis is a spiritual community that ho
 nors the body’s wisdom and lived experience. Whether you’re healing fr
 om religious trauma\, deconstructing beliefs\, exploring spirituality\, or
  just want to be with other conscious persons\, this space is for you.\n\n
 Expect conscious conversations\, meditation\, breathwork\, sound healing\,
  and other somatic practices to help reconnect with ourselves and each oth
 er.\n\nwe share a potluck dinner every last Monday of the month.\n\n📅 *
 *Date & Time**: Mondays 6-8 PM\n📍 **Location**: 727 T St. Sacramento\, 
 Ca\, 95811\n💜 **All our events are free\, donations supported.**\n✨ *
 *No prior experience or spiritual beliefs necessary.**\n📩 **RSVP/ Quest
 ions? Reach out at** embody.iama@gmail.com\n🔗 **Follow us on Instagram:
 ** [@embody.iama](https://www.instagram.com/embody.iama)\n\nPS: we meet in
  the social hall of Parkview Presbyterian Church. Please find us through t
 he back entrance\, the brown gate on Solons alley. You may park in the bac
 k\, move the orange post to park and please return it when you leave.
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/mindful-embodied-spirituality/events/
 bgfpxtyjckbjb/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260521T032327Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260521T032327Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
